## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2d7e5-103">Il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> controllo offre le funzionalità seguenti:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d7e5-103">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> control provides the following capabilities:</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2d7e5-104">**Navigazione**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A>e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d7e5-104">**Navigation**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2d7e5-105">**Durata della navigazione**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d7e5-105">**Navigation Lifetime**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.</span></span>  
  
